# Site-specific secret patterns for the pre-commit hook.
#
# Copy to `patterns.local` (gitignored) and fill in YOUR real values. This
# example file is committed; patterns.local is not — that split exists because
# the first version of the hook committed the real literals to a public repo,
# which leaked the very things it was written to protect.
#
# Format: label|extended-regex — one per line. Remember to escape dots in
# hostnames and IDs, or `.` matches any character.
#
# NAS username|myusername@|/Users/myusername|homes/myusername
# tailnet name|mytailnet[a-z0-9]+
# Komga library ID|MYLIBRARYID123
# NAS SSH port|(-p|Port)[[:space:]]+12345
